edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d4db65991486598ef71c3242f0b9905efca6a46e","tid":1521622,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"99f680cc82aac2b36aa164e0b68aaf4f48f83417","tid":1521622,"uid":207390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2a463e173d35021b721c4e918e7adc8420c7f1a7","tid":1521622,"uid":277540,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"應對 #顏料水<br />\n<br />\n特性<br />\n染料入面有稀釋左嘅 聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯 Acrylici 成份，乾左之後會好難洗甩，就咁揾水無用，一定要盡快清洗<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n包全身，完事棄裝<br />\n- 頭：先用衫 #包頭 、頭盔、眼罩、口罩 <br />\n- 頸、手：保鮮紙<br />\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},{"pid":"f44b75225c8450afd1d011dda0b41f60b4ccbffc","tid":1521622,"uid":210707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7006dc2ddb57a0bfd9e4e91c56c8d01861271135","tid":1521622,"uid":98763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:11:02.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"8e17126a684641448a3aec58af9d24be8900ec7b","tid":1521622,"uid":177510,"like":0,"dislike":0