>\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e205d30ca0fff6834e8354af9293d3472f5f732","tid":1521622,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c336ab1d22fa15fa6f9fca96f47ec54cc472aea5","tid":1521622,"uid":78968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d0db45fa564a103ea8ad90dc900cc89d3566f24","tid":1521622,"uid":31720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abcebf99d534ea114d8c85f0579167934b0bb6cc","tid":1521622,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8014189ec3450105a4ea56a048a2a1c82c2af3f","tid":1521622,"uid":305068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1854f18aaa260f6ba024ebafc055e63596957886","tid":1521622,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"儘量避開CCTV,<br />\n搭車用散紙,<br />\n買新的長衫長褲(或者帽)返屋企"},{"pid":"1d8ac006e9c68ab3ff74e3c283fee7fd6b5d39d6","tid":1521622,"uid":305068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fb36074341d9dbdc62619ae481e9179e00b29e0","tid":1521622,"uid":305068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f