" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0249a5a41b7a47a4f4e701ed61b127379f50aca","tid":1521622,"uid":56301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4290064e1e33248726f389e611f4c655ec09a10f","tid":1521622,"uid":179177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"應對 #顏料水<br />\n<br />\n特性<br />\n染料入面有稀釋左嘅 聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯 Acrylici 成份，乾左之後會好難洗甩，就咁揾水無用，一定要盡快清洗<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n包全身，完事棄裝<br />\n- 頭：先用衫 #包頭 、頭盔、眼罩、口罩 <br />\n- 頸、手：保鮮紙<br />\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},{"pid":"ccbfbeef8dd13df9b2c770b2a1f1cde13f66efb5","tid":1521622,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e87748da26a78db3168dfb147d3a42ef516404f","tid":1521622,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4290064e1e33248726f389e611f4c655ec09a10f","tid":1521622,"uid":179177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"應對 #顏料水<br />\n<br />\n特性<br />\n染料入面有稀釋左嘅 聚甲基丙烯酸甲酯 Acrylici 成份，乾左之後會好難洗甩，就咁揾水無用，一定要盡快清洗<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n包全身，完事棄裝<br />\n- 頭：先用衫 #包頭 、頭盔、眼罩、口罩 <br />\n- 頸、手：保鮮紙<br />\n- 身：全可即棄black bloc<br />\n- 鞋：即棄鞋、拎多對<br />\n- 重要：最上層要着件防水外套／雨褸<br />\n<br />\n皮膚<br />\n方法一：醋 + 水 (比例1:3)<br />\n將手浸喺醋水約5分鐘，要邊浸邊捽<br />\n<br />\n方法二：蘇打粉 + 溫水 (比例1:1)<br />\n蘇打粉水要攪勻，最好係用流動溫水邊沖邊捽，來回倒五六次就得<br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟身上面中左好多染色劑，要揾個浴缸浸落去！<br />\n<br />\n衣物<br />\n方法一：氨水（即係阿摩尼亞水）<br />\n用氨水浸15分鐘，然後再用冷水浸15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n方法二：棄掉染色衣物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ce8b55bad21169963e5430b6809101309f7033","tid":1521622,"uid":136382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b30cd290d239858b0ff88f127e92a257723d001d","tid":1521622,"uid":92879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c38279eaf27f008dc16863fba437073f8c8600","tid":1521622,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1241d6e9d4d42079470368354c780516f0b6a4","tid":1521622,"uid":240522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d09bc0bc267ea8c47316d997cb764a16094ba80c","tid":1521622,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"dai dai lik tui"},{"pid":"2c2bc5adbd066b108496aba4bd80c056c2c0c951","tid":1521622,"uid":102120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9666a5361fe0cafb12aa78c9f247ffa0c0ec4b43","tid":1521622,"uid":248317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"